Commands:

1.Create a directory where terraform hellow world file will be created
- mkdir Terraform

2.Create a terraform file
- vi hellow-world.tf

3.Code in hellow-world.tf file
--> 
// this is comment
# this is also comment

output hello {
     value = "Hellow World Sonal!!"
}

4.Command to view file creates : ls

5.Run the plan command inside the directory where this hellow-world.tf file is situated
- terraform plan

Terraform plan command basically tells us what all changes will be applied when you'll run terraform apply



